| 7 | Part def Engine | **Yes** | Present as 'ConfigurableEngine'. |
| 8 | Engine has part 'cylinder' : Cylinder[2..*] | **Partial** | 'cylinders : Cylinder[4..6]' (multiplicity is [4..6] instead of [2..*]). |
| 9 | Part '4cylEngine' : Engine | **Yes** | 'FourCylinderEngine :> ConfigurableEngine'. |
| 10 | '4cylEngine' redefines cylinder[4] | **Yes** | 'FourCylinderEngine' redefines 'cylinders[4]'. |
| 11 | Part '6cylEngine' : Engine | **Yes** | 'SixCylinderEngine :> ConfigurableEngine'. |
| 12 | '6cylEngine' redefines cylinder[6] | **Yes** | 'SixCylinderEngine' redefines 'cylinders[6]'. |
| 13 | Variation attribute def DiameterChoices :> Diameter | **Partial** | 'SmallDiameterCylinder' and 'LargeDiameterCylinder' specialize 'Cylinder' with diameter values, but not as a variation attribute. |
| 14 | DiameterChoices has variant 'diameterSmall' = 70[mm] | **Yes** | 'SmallDiameterCylinder' redefines diameter = 70[mm]. |
| 15 | DiameterChoices has variant 'diameterLarge' = 100[mm] | **Yes** | 'LargeDiameterCylinder' redefines diameter = 100[mm]. |
| 16 | Variation part def EngineChoices :> Engine | **Partial** | No explicit variation part, but 'FourCylinderEngine' and 'SixCylinderEngine' exist. |
| 17 | EngineChoices has variant '4cylEngine' | **Yes** | 'FourCylinderEngine' exists. |
| 18 | EngineChoices has variant '6cylEngine' | **Yes** | 'SixCylinderEngine' exists. |
